name: Zillow Metrics (Cities): Homes Foreclosed (Out of 10k) - Valinda, CA
description: The number of homes per 10,000 that were foreclosed in a given month. A foreclosure is when a homeowner loses their home to their lending institution or it is sold to a third party at an auction. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
